sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Service as modelmesh-serving Service<br/>ClusterIP
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy Container<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>MLServer/Triton/OpenVINO
    participant Puller as Storage Puller<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Etcd as Etcd Service<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraping

    Note over Client,Prom: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Service: POST /inference.GRPCInferenceService<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>No Auth
    Service->>ModelMesh: Forward request<br/>gRPC
    ModelMesh->>ModelServer: Route to appropriate model<br/>8001-8090/TCP gRPC
    ModelServer-->>ModelMesh: Inference result
    ModelMesh-->>Service: Response
    Service-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,Prom: Flow 2: REST Inference Request

    Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8008/TCP HTTP<br/>No Auth
    Service->>RESTProxy: Forward HTTP request<br/>8008/TCP
    RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    ModelMesh->>ModelServer: Route to model<br/>8001-8090/TCP gRPC
    ModelServer-->>ModelMesh: Inference result
    ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>Service: Translate to HTTP
    Service-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Prom: Flow 3: Model Loading from S3

    Puller->>S3: GET /bucket/model-path<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS Access Keys
    S3-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller->>Puller: Write to shared volume<br/>emptyDir
    ModelServer->>ModelServer: Load model from<br/>shared volume

    Note over Client,Prom: Flow 4: Controller Reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: CR event notification
    Controller->>Etcd: Update cluster state<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS 1.2+ mTLS/Password
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate ServingRuntime<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Prom: Flow 5: Metrics Collection

    Prom->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller-->>Prom: Controller metrics
    Prom->>Service: GET /metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP<br/>No Auth
    Service->>ModelMesh: Forward to runtime pod
    ModelMesh-->>Prom: Runtime metrics
